Description:
By request, I am uploading Yes's "Going for the One Studio Sessions". 
This DVD documents the recording of their 1977 album: Going for the 
One. Legend has it that the taping of these sessions was to be made 
into a feature-length film. The video and audio quality are good. 
Cover art and screenshots have been included. The audio and
video have NOT been altered - in any way. Thanks to Zerosun666 
for the source.

Details for the Going for the One album: 
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Going_for_the_One

Links to GFTO tour dates on Forgotten Yesterdays: 
http://forgotten-yesterdays.com/tours.asp?ftype=1&qtourid=8


Cast:
Jon Anderson - vocals, harp and guitar
Steve Howe - guitars and vocals
Chris Squire - bass, guitar and vocals
Rick Wakeman - keyboards
Alan White - percussion and vocals
